me biomass composition during all the experimental time. Thus, this\nstudy showed that the dominance of cyanobacteria in microalgal based wastewater\ntreatment systems can be controlled by the operational and nutritional\nconditions. This knowledge could contribute to control microalgae contamination\nfrom up-scaling cyanobacterial biomass production in wastewater treatment\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 22 Dec 2018 16:38:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-27"}
