rage angle errors are at\nmost of 1.1${\\deg}$. It is feasible to integrate an EM tracking sensor to an\nenergy independent plastic scintillation dosimeter with minimal impact to the\ncollected signal as well as sufficient positional accuracy to keep dose\nuncertainty below 5${\\%}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 22 Dec 2018 22:04:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-27"}
