 in fact more generally, of\ngeneral Rockland operators on general graded groups. As a by-product, we\nrecover the Sobolev embeddings on graded groups established in [FiRu17], and\nobtain explicit hypoelliptic heat semigroup estimates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 22 Dec 2018 23:04:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-27"}
