est of our knowledge, this work\nrepresents the first quantitative attempt at characterizing verified users on\nTwitter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 23 Dec 2018 13:45:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Dec 2018 08:49:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 12 Mar 2019 13:03:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-13"}
